SZ|002861|<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="pragma" CONTENT="no-cache">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="Cache-Control" CONTENT="no-cache, must-revalidate">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="expires" CONTENT="0">
<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170323172010" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170323172010" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170323172010"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170323172010"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170323172010"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002861";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

			}
		});

<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331183746" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331183746"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331183746"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331183746"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002847";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002840";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002832";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331184129"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331184129"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331184129"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002826";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	<div class="wrapper">

			<div class="content">

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();

			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002819";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170331184753" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331184753" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331184753"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331184753"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331184753"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002812";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002798";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002783";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>

<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331185152" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331185152"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331185152"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002770";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

	var gpdm = "SZ002763";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

SZ|002756|<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="pragma" CONTENT="no-cache">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="Cache-Control" CONTENT="no-cache, must-revalidate">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="expires" CONTENT="0">
<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170401033637" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170401033637" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170401033637"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170401033637"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170401033637"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002756";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331183603"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331183603"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002749";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002741";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331183917"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331183917"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331183917"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002735";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002728";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331183855" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331183855"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331183855"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331183855"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002722";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002715";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>

<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="pragma" CONTENT="no-cache">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="Cache-Control" CONTENT="no-cache, must-revalidate">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="expires" CONTENT="0">
<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170331185631" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331185631" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331185631"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331185631"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331185631"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002709";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	<div class="wrapper">

	function showStocks(gntc) {

			if (textStatus == "error") {

			}
		});
	};

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002695";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();

			dropbox.hide();

<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331185426" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331185426"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331185426"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002682";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

	var gpdm = "SZ002676";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331183456"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002669";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331190137"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002663";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

<title>操盘必读</title>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002656";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331185122"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331185122"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002650";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	<div class="wrapper">

		<script type="text/javascript" src="../index/SZ002650_B0.js?v=20170331185122"></script>

			<div class="content">

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002643";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331183813" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331183813"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331183813"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331183813"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002637";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002630";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>

<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="pragma" CONTENT="no-cache">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="Cache-Control" CONTENT="no-cache, must-revalidate">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="expires" CONTENT="0">
<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170331185904" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331185904" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331185904"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331185904"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331185904"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002624";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	<div class="wrapper">

	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002617";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002611";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}

<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="pragma" CONTENT="no-cache">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="Cache-Control" CONTENT="no-cache, must-revalidate">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="expires" CONTENT="0">
<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170331184241" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331184241" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331184241"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331184241"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331184241"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002598";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

	var gpdm = "SZ002592";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="pragma" CONTENT="no-cache">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="Cache-Control" CONTENT="no-cache, must-revalidate">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="expires" CONTENT="0">
<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170331182841" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331182841" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331182841"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331182841"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331182841"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002585";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331182325"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331182325"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002579";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	<div class="wrapper">

			<div class="content">

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002572";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331184334"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331184334"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331184334"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002566";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	function showStocks(gntc) {

		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");

	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");

			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002559";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170331182546" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331182546" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331182546"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331182546"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331182546"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002553";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	var gpdm = "SZ002546";

		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",

			perPage : 10,

		});

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002540";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002527";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>

<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331185007"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331185007"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002514";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="pragma" CONTENT="no-cache">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="Cache-Control" CONTENT="no-cache, must-revalidate">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="expires" CONTENT="0">
<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170401034117" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170401034117" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170401034117"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170401034117"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170401034117"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002501";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331182042"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002495";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>
