<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002488";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170401044449"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170401044449"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002482";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	<div class="wrapper">

		<script type="text/javascript" src="../index/SZ002482_B0.js?v=20170401044449"></script>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002475";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331184605"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331184605"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331184605"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002469";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002462";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<meta HTTP-EQUIV="Cache-Control" CONTENT="no-cache, must-revalidate">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="expires" CONTENT="0">
<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170331182720" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331182720" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331182720"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331182720"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331182720"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002456";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002449";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002443";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

				box.unload();

		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});

			delay : 0

<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331184053" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331184053"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331184053"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002430";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

	var gpdm = "SZ002424";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

SZ|002417|<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="pragma" CONTENT="no-cache">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="Cache-Control" CONTENT="no-cache, must-revalidate">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="expires" CONTENT="0">
<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170331182134" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331182134" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331182134"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331182134"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331182134"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002417";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331185716"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331185716"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002411";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

			<div class="content">

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002404";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331183904"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331183904"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331183904"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002398";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	<div class="wrapper">

	function pagination(top, left) {

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002391";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331182649" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331182649"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331182649"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331182649"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002385";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002378";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>

<meta HTTP-EQUIV="pragma" CONTENT="no-cache">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="Cache-Control" CONTENT="no-cache, must-revalidate">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="expires" CONTENT="0">
<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170331182355" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331182355" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331182355"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331182355"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331182355"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002372";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002365";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002359";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002346";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002333";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002327";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	<div class="wrapper">

		<script type="text/javascript" src="../index/SZ002327_B0.js?v=20170331185356"></script>
		<div class='dzh_secondindex'></div>
		<div class="scrollInner">
			<div class="content">
				<div class="wrap">

SZ|002320|<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="pragma" CONTENT="no-cache">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="Cache-Control" CONTENT="no-cache, must-revalidate">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="expires" CONTENT="0">
<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170331211718" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331211718" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331211718"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331211718"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331211718"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002320";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331183852"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331183852"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002314";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

			<div class="content">

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002307";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331182547"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331182547"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331182547"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002301";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002294";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<meta HTTP-EQUIV="Cache-Control" CONTENT="no-cache, must-revalidate">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="expires" CONTENT="0">
<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170331183852" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331183852" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331183852"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331183852"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331183852"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002288";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002281";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002275";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}

<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170401042521" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170401042521"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170401042521"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002262";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170401153159" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170401153159"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170401153159"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002249";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002243";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

SZ|002236|<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="pragma" CONTENT="no-cache">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="Cache-Control" CONTENT="no-cache, must-revalidate">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="expires" CONTENT="0">
<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170401033819" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170401033819" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170401033819"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170401033819"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170401033819"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002236";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331185509"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331185509"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002230";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	<div class="wrapper">

			<div class="content">

<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002223";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170401044447"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170401044447"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170401044447"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002217";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

			<div class="content">

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002210";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170401043654" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170401043654" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170401043654"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170401043654"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170401043654"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002204";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	function showStocks(gntc) {

		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();

			dropbox.hide();

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002191";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002178";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}

<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331185938"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331185938"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002165";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="pragma" CONTENT="no-cache">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="Cache-Control" CONTENT="no-cache, must-revalidate">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="expires" CONTENT="0">
<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170331183058" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331183058" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331183058"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331183058"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331183058"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002152";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331182857"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331182857"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002146";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002139";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331184457"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331184457"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331184457"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002133";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	<div class="wrapper">

		<script type="text/javascript" src="../index/SZ002133_B0.js?v=20170331184457"></script>

			<div class="content">
