<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002126";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170331185444" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331185444" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331185444"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331185444"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331185444"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002120";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002107";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();

<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331184917" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331184917"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331184917"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002094";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331182603"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331182603"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002081";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002075";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

<html>

<meta HTTP-EQUIV="pragma" CONTENT="no-cache">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="Cache-Control" CONTENT="no-cache, must-revalidate">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="expires" CONTENT="0">
<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170331182048" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331182048" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331182048"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331182048"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331182048"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002068";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331184922"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331184922"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002062";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	<div class="wrapper">

		<script type="text/javascript" src="../index/SZ002062_B0.js?v=20170331184922"></script>

			<div class="content">

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002055";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331183658"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331183658"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331183658"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002049";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002042";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>

<meta HTTP-EQUIV="Cache-Control" CONTENT="no-cache, must-revalidate">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="expires" CONTENT="0">
<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170331183657" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331183657" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331183657"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331183657"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331183657"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002036";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002029";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}

<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331184910"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002023";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ002010";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>

<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331184448" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331184448"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331184448"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000999";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000982";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000976";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

SZ|000968|<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="pragma" CONTENT="no-cache">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="Cache-Control" CONTENT="no-cache, must-revalidate">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="expires" CONTENT="0">
<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170331185324" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331185324" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331185324"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331185324"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331185324"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000968";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170401033752"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170401033752"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000961";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	<div class="wrapper">

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000953";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331182539"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331182539"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331182539"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000939";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	<div class="wrapper">

		<script type="text/javascript" src="../index/SZ000939_B0.js?v=20170331182539"></script>

			<div class="content">

<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000931";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170331185553" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331185553" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331185553"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331185553"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331185553"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000925";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({

<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331185711" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331185711"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331185711"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331185711"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000910";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000893";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

	var gpdm = "SZ000886";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

SZ|000877|<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="pragma" CONTENT="no-cache">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="Cache-Control" CONTENT="no-cache, must-revalidate">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="expires" CONTENT="0">
<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170331183356" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331183356" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331183356"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331183356"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331183356"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000877";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331185351"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331185351"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000863";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	<div class="wrapper">

		<script type="text/javascript" src="../index/SZ000863_B0.js?v=20170331185351"></script>

			<div class="content">

<title>操盘必读</title>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000852";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170401033749"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170401033749"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170401033749"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000837";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000829";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<meta HTTP-EQUIV="Cache-Control" CONTENT="no-cache, must-revalidate">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="expires" CONTENT="0">
<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170331182850" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331182850" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331182850"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331182850"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331182850"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000822";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000815";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000807";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

				box.unload();
			} else {

			}
		});
	};

		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({

			first : "<<",last:">>",

			firstTitle : "首页",

			perPage : 10,

			delay : 0

<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331230817" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331230817"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331230817"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000792";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000777";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000765";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	<div class="wrapper">

		<script type="text/javascript" src="../index/SZ000765_B0.js?v=20170322070034"></script>
		<div class='dzh_secondindex'></div>
		<div class="scrollInner">
			<div class="content">

SZ|000757|<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="pragma" CONTENT="no-cache">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="Cache-Control" CONTENT="no-cache, must-revalidate">
<meta HTTP-EQUIV="expires" CONTENT="0">
<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170331184629" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331184629" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331184629"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331184629"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331184629"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000757";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331185107"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331185107"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000750";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	<div class="wrapper">

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000733";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331184217"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331184217"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331184217"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000727";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

	<div class="wrapper">

<title>操盘必读</title>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000719";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

<link type="text/css" media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/f10style.css?v=20170331182515" id="stylefile" />
<link href="../../css/cjhbStyle.css?v=20170331182515" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>操盘必读</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-1.8.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common.js?v=20170331182515"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jPages.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/date.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/cpbd.js?v=20170331182515"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331182515"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000712";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
<body>

		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/f10_secondIndex.js?v=20170331182443"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000697";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
