				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000681";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}

<title>操盘必读</title>

<script type="text/javascript">
	var blockid = 1;
	var _paq = _paq || [];
	var gpdm = "SZ000667";
	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>

	$(function() {
		bindEvent(gpdm, blockid);
		bindAd();
	});

	function showStocks(gntc) {
		var box = $("#gntc_stockbox");
		var zscode = gntc.attr("id");
		var path = "gntc/" + zscode + ".html .dropbox";
		var o = gntc.offset();

		box.load(path, function(responseText, textStatus, XMLHttpRequest) {
			if (textStatus == "error") {
				box.unload();
			} else {
				pagination(o.top,o.left);
			}
		});
	};

	function pagination(top, left) {
		var dropbox = $(".dropbox");
		var dbPagenav = $(".dbPagenav");

		dropbox.attr("style", "top: " + (top - 370) + "px;left:" + (left) + "px;").toggle();
		$("#tcss" + " tr").removeClass("jp-hidden").removeAttr("style");
		dropbox.click(function(event) {
			event = event || window.event;
			event.stopPropagation();
		});
		$(document).click(function(e) {
			dropbox.hide();
		});
		dbPagenav.jPages({
			containerID : "tcss",
			first : "<<",last:">>",
			previous : "<-",next:"->",
			firstTitle : "首页",
			previousTitle : "上一页",
			nextTitle : "下一页",
			lastTitle : "最后一页",
			midRange : 4,
			perPage : 10,
			fallback : 0,
			delay : 0
		});
	}
	
	
</script>
</head>
